name: BMO All-Equity ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to provide the potential for long term capital appreciation. To achieve investment objective the Fund primarily by investing in ETFs that provide exposure to a diversified portfolio of global equity securities. The ETF will employ a strategic asset allocation strategy and is expected to primarily invest in equity securities through investing in other BMO ETFs. As an alternative to or in conjunction with investing directly in ETFs, exposure may be obtained by investing directly in equity securities, in mutual funds and or in derivative instruments.
